The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, paramedic
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Job   | paramedic   | designer   |
| Transport     | train       | ship      |

