1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk       |
| Hobby      | traveling     | skydiving  |
| City        | marseilles          | san-francisco |

